CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Two Rivals - William Vick, left, and Robert Scott will be halfback rivals for the opposing sides.  Scott is a Connellsville ace, and weights 198 pounds.  Vick, Braddock, pulls 190 pounds... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County All-Star Jaycee football player no. 18 William Vick, and Western Pennsylvania All-Star Jaycee football player no. 8 Robert Scott, standing on field
